## 6. Top Hiring Companies

### 6.1 Companies with Most Job Openings

Identifying top hiring companies helps job seekers target organizations with multiple opportunities.

::: {#c1902c54 .cell execution_count=11}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# Get top 15 companies by job postings
company_counts = df['COMPANY_NAME'].value_counts().head(15)
company_df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Company': company_counts.index,
    'Job Postings': company_counts.values
})

# Create horizontal bar chart
company_df.hvplot.barh(
    x='Company',
    y='Job Postings',
    title='Top 15 Companies by Number of Job Postings (2024)',
    height=700,
    width=900,
    color='#e74c3c',
    ylabel='',
    xlabel='Number of Job Postings',
    flip_yaxis=True
)
